    <title>amd黑苹果docker折腾记录</title>
    <url>/2020/08/17/RyzenHackintoshDocker/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="amd黑苹果docker折腾记录"><a href="#amd黑苹果docker折腾记录" class="headerlink" title="amd黑苹果docker折腾记录"></a>amd黑苹果docker折腾记录</h1><p>虽然AMD黑苹果目前无法使用VMware、PD和docker desktop之类的使用英特尔CPU虚拟华技术的应用，但听说基于virtualbox的docker toolbox还是能用的，我就打算安个docker toolbox来用。没想到坑是真的多。下面讲讲我的安装和使用经历。</p>
<h2 id="配置"><a href="#配置" class="headerlink" title="配置"></a>配置</h2><p>本人黑苹果硬件配置为Ryzen 3700x + Asus Prime x570-p，显卡是rx 570，580 2048sp刷的，网卡intel ax200。系统版本10.15.6，引导是oc 0.5.7</p>
<h2 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h2><p>bios虚拟化先打开，然后去<a href="https://docs.docker.com/toolbox/toolbox_install_mac/">https://docs.docker.com/toolbox/toolbox_install_mac/</a> 下载最新的mac版docker toolbox安装。本来以为万事大吉，结果quickstart terminal报错启动不了：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Error with pre-create check: &quot;This computer doesn&#39;t have VT-X&#x2F;AMD-v enabled. Enabling it in the BIOS is mandatory&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>发现时创建docker-machine时会执行虚拟化开关检查。但貌似mac的dockermachine不支持amd-v？开了也会报错，然后<code>docker-machine create --help</code>一下试试：</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Usage: docker-machine create [OPTIONS] [arg...]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Create a machine</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Description:</span><br><span class="line">   Run &#39;docker-machine create --driver name --help&#39; to include the create flags for that driver in the help text.</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Options:</span><br><span class="line">   </span><br><span class="line">   --driver, -d &quot;virtualbox&quot;                                        Driver to create machine with. [$MACHINE_DRIVER]</span><br><span class="line">   --engine-env [--engine-env option --engine-env option]                        Specify environment variables to set in the engine</span><br><span class="line">   --engine-insecure-registry [--engine-insecure-registry option --engine-insecure-registry option]    Specify insecure registries to allow with the created engine</span><br><span class="line">   --engine-install-url &quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;get.docker.com&quot;                            Custom URL to use for engine installation [$MACHINE_DOCKER_INSTALL_URL]</span><br><span class="line">   --engine-label [--engine-label option --engine-label option]                        Specify labels for the created engine</span><br><span class="line">   --engine-opt [--engine-opt option --engine-opt option]                        Specify arbitrary flags to include with the created engine in the form flag&#x3D;value</span><br><span class="line">   --engine-registry-mirror [--engine-registry-mirror option --engine-registry-mirror option]        Specify registry mirrors to use [$ENGINE_REGISTRY_MIRROR]</span><br><span class="line">   --engine-storage-driver                                         Specify a storage driver to use with the engine</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm                                                Configure Machine to join a Swarm cluster</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-addr                                             addr to advertise for Swarm (default: detect and use the machine IP)</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-discovery                                             Discovery service to use with Swarm</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-experimental                                            Enable Swarm experimental features</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-host &quot;tcp:&#x2F;&#x2F;0.0.0.0:3376&quot;                                    ip&#x2F;socket to listen on for Swarm master</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-image &quot;swarm:latest&quot;                                        Specify Docker image to use for Swarm [$MACHINE_SWARM_IMAGE]</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-join-opt [--swarm-join-opt option --swarm-join-opt option]                    Define arbitrary flags for Swarm join</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-master                                            Configure Machine to be a Swarm master</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-opt [--swarm-opt option --swarm-opt option]                            Define arbitrary flags for Swarm master</span><br><span class="line">   --swarm-strategy &quot;spread&quot;                                        Define a default scheduling strategy for Swarm</span><br><span class="line">   --tls-san [--tls-san option --tls-san option]                            Support extra SANs for TLS certs</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-boot2docker-url                                     The URL of the boot2docker image. Defaults to the latest available version [$VIRTUALBOX_BOOT2DOCKER_URL]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-cpu-count &quot;1&quot;                                        number of CPUs for the machine (-1 to use the number of CPUs available) [$VIRTUALBOX_CPU_COUNT]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-disk-size &quot;20000&quot;                                    Size of disk for host in MB [$VIRTUALBOX_DISK_SIZE]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-host-dns-resolver                                    Use the host DNS resolver [$VIRTUALBOX_HOST_DNS_RESOLVER]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-hostonly-cidr &quot;192.168.99.1&#x2F;24&quot;                                Specify the Host Only CIDR [$VIRTUALBOX_HOSTONLY_CIDR]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-hostonly-nicpromisc &quot;deny&quot;                                Specify the Host Only Network Adapter Promiscuous Mode [$VIRTUALBOX_HOSTONLY_NIC_PROMISC]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-hostonly-nictype &quot;82540EM&quot;                                Specify the Host Only Network Adapter Type [$VIRTUALBOX_HOSTONLY_NIC_TYPE]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-hostonly-no-dhcp                                    Disable the Host Only DHCP Server [$VIRTUALBOX_HOSTONLY_NO_DHCP]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-import-boot2docker-vm                                     The name of a Boot2Docker VM to import [$VIRTUALBOX_BOOT2DOCKER_IMPORT_VM]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-memory &quot;1024&quot;                                        Size of memory for host in MB [$VIRTUALBOX_MEMORY_SIZE]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-nat-nictype &quot;82540EM&quot;                                    Specify the Network Adapter Type [$VIRTUALBOX_NAT_NICTYPE]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-no-dns-proxy                                        Disable proxying all DNS requests to the host [$VIRTUALBOX_NO_DNS_PROXY]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-no-share                                        Disable the mount of your home directory [$VIRTUALBOX_NO_SHARE]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-no-vtx-check                                        Disable checking for the availability of hardware virtualization before the vm is started [$VIRTUALBOX_NO_VTX_CHECK]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-share-folder                                         Mount the specified directory instead of the default home location. Format: dir:name [$VIRTUALBOX_SHARE_FOLDER]</span><br><span class="line">   --virtualbox-ui-type &quot;headless&quot;                                    Specify the UI Type: (gui|sdl|headless|separate) [$VIRTUALBOX_UI_TYPE]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>发现有一个选项<code>--virtualbox-no-vtx-check</code>，禁用硬件虚拟化检查。果断加上这个参数手动创建<code>default</code>虚拟机：</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><figcaption><span>script</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker-machine create default --virtualbox-no-vtx-check</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>正常来讲应该成功了。不过它会去github下载Boot2Docker.iso，下载速度感人，于是我手动去<a href="https://github.com/boot2docker/boot2docker/releases">https://github.com/boot2docker/boot2docker/releases</a> 下载了ios包放到<code>～/.docker/machine/cache/</code>下面就可以从本地读取了。<br>接下来运行quickstart terminal就一切正常了！</p>
<h2 id="使用"><a href="#使用" class="headerlink" title="使用"></a>使用</h2><p>为了方便正常使用命令行，可以设置以下环境变量：</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><figcaption><span>script</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">export DOCKER_HOST=tcp://192.168.99.100:2376</span><br><span class="line">export DOCKER_MACHINE_NAME=default</span><br><span class="line">export DOCKER_TLS_VERIFY=1</span><br><span class="line">export DOCKER_CERT_PATH=/Users/geyinchi/.docker/machine/machines/default</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>如果<code>～/.docker/machine/machines/default</code>下面没有相关证书，就把<code>～/.docker/machine/certs</code>下面文件都拷过去（应该不用都拷过去，懒得分辨了）</p>
</blockquote>
<p>我把上面四行写在了<code>~/.bash_profile</code>里，发现不自动生效还要source一下，后来想起来macos要写在<code>~/.zshrc</code>里。干脆在<code>~/.zshrc</code>加了一行<code>source ~/.bash_profile</code><br>运行docker ps看一下：</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><figcaption><span>script</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(base) geyinchi@geyinchis-Mac-Pro ~ % docker ps</span><br><span class="line">CONTAINER ID        IMAGE               COMMAND             CREATED             STATUS              PORTS               NAMES</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>熟悉的界面出来了，搞定！</p>
<h2 id="坑"><a href="#坑" class="headerlink" title="坑"></a>坑</h2><p>一次新建容器需要挂载volumes，结果发现挂载进去的目录下面是空的。百度了半天都说的是默认只能挂载<code>/Users</code>目录。但我确实是在桌面建的。后来发现原来还需要手动去虚拟机里挂载共享目录。去virtualbox新建共享文件夹，比如我在桌面新建了个docker文件夹专门用来放docker容器所需文件的，到default虚拟机设置里设置一下共享文件夹。</p>
<p><a href="RyzenHackintoshDocker/virtualbox.png">img</a></p>
<p>然后去虚拟机里，可以从virtualbox进，或者直接<code>docker-machine ssh default</code>进入命令行。</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><figcaption><span>script</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd /</span><br><span class="line">sudo mkdir docker</span><br><span class="line">sudo mount -t vboxsf docker[virtualbox共享文件夹的名称] /docker[要挂载的位置]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>然后docker容器启动参数里宿主机目录位置就可以写/docker/…了，比如我的docker-compose.yml：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">version:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;2&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">services:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">nginx:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">always</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">nginx:latest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="number">80</span><span class="string">:80</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">/docker/nginx/conf.d:/etc/nginx/conf.d</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">/docker/nginx/log:/var/log/nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">/docker/nginx/html:/etc/nginx/html</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>ps：也尝试过直接挂载/Users，结果挂载各种权限问题。甚至还要去下载我onedrive文件夹的数据。那还是算了吧，挂载一个文件夹够了。</p>
<p>暂时告一段落了。docker使用基本都正常了。以后有问题再继续吧。toolbox不好的地方就在容器服务的ip都要192.168.99.100（默认），除非去virtualbox端口转发。略麻烦</p>
]]></content>
